All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
FYPCoordinator
FYP Coordinator class containing an individual FYP Coordinator's attributes and functions, extended from Supervisor
FYPCoordinatorDatabase
FYPCoordinatorDatabase class holds all FYP Coordinator objects, and initialises program from CSV database each startup
FYPCoordinatorUI
Contains the layout and functions when an FYP Coordinator logs in
Input_cleaner
Class that performs input cleaning to prevent program from crashing in the event of InputMismatch
Main
Creates a new scanner, studentDatabase, supervisorDatabase, projectDatabase, requestDatabase and FYPCoordinatorDatabase objects
Project
Project class defining the creation of Project objects and its functions
ProjectDatabase
ProjectDatabase class holds all projects, and initialises program from CSV database each startup
ProjectState
Enumerator to set the Project State of a Project object Project
Request
Request class defining the creation of all 4 types of requests objects (Register, Deregister, Title Change and Student Transfer) and its print function RequestType
RequestDatabase
RequestDatabase class holds all Request objects, initialises program from CSV database each startup and handles Project object management
RequestType
Enumerator to set the Request Type of a Request object Request
Student
Student class containing an individual student's attributes and functions, extended from User superclass
StudentDatabase
StudentDatabase class holds all Student objects, initialises program from CSV database each startup
StudentUI
Contains the layout and functions when a student logs in
SupervDatabase
SupervDatabase class holds all supervisor objects, and initialises program from CSV database each startup
Supervisor
Supervisor class containing an individual supervisor's attributes and functions
SupervisorUI
Contains the layout and functions when a supervisor logs in
UI
 
User
User class containing basic user attributes applicable to all users, like their First + Last name, userID, password, and full email
Util
Utility classes that are called in main to verify entered credentials and updates all CSV databases upon logout
